Text: Re Summer QA Cc Attached are updates to the HR piece indicated in red Janie Karen NRON AM To Steven J ES John AmblerENRON NRONDEVELOPMENT Dennis VegasENRON NRONDEVELOPMENT Johan ZaaymanENRON NRONDEVELOPMENT Keith nron Richard LeibertENRON NRONDEVELOPMENT Janie BonnardENRON NRONDEVELOPMENT Miguel nron Mary NRON Aaron NRON Richard ES Henry MeansENRON NRONDEVELOPMENT cc Subject Summer QA Attached is the latest draft QA document which Ive edited and attempted to organize into topics There are a number of questions that still need answers Ive also attached a draft of the key messages Please let me know if you have any additions comments or changes to either document by the end of the day Thursday Thank you Karen
